# RQ-53-20-03-050: Weight Target 4.67 kg/m²

## Requirement Statement
The BWB outer skin panels shall not exceed weight target of 4.67 kg/m² (2,100 kg total).

## Rationale
Weight control essential for aircraft performance and fuel efficiency.

## Acceptance Criteria
- Panel weight ≤ 4.67 kg/m² (as-built)
- Total skin panel weight ≤ 2,100 kg
- Weight tracked through manufacturing

## Compliance Status
Estimated weight 4.52 kg/m² (3% under target)

## Traceability
Parent: Aircraft-level weight budget
